    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='158:184'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '012-1a' );" name="012-1a" class="pb">[012-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='184:192'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='192:204'>　周易章句證異卷十二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='204:225'>　　　　　　　　　　　内閣中書翟均㢘撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='225:231'>雜卦𫝊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='231:245'>　熊朋來襍從衣集聲俗作雜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='245:269'>　鄭𤣥曰舊次在序卦後韓伯及吕大防諸儒同惟俞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='269:287'>　琰在說卦後序卦前　鄭𤣥無雜卦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='287:297'>乾剛坤柔比樂師憂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='297:323'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '012-1b' );" name="012-1b" class="pb">[012-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='323:333'>臨觀之義或與或求</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='333:346'>屯見而不失其居蒙雜而著</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='346:383'>　雜鄭𤣥作稚<span class='krp-note'>云稚誤作雜當蒙昩㓜稚之/時心无所定非叢雜之義</span>　著張子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='383:390'>　曰古著字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='390:405'>震起也艮止也損益盛衰之始也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='405:415'>大畜時也无妄災也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='415:430'>萃聚而升不來也謙輕而豫怠也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='430:466'>　怠京房作治　虞翻作怡也<span class='krp-note'>云豫薦樂祖考故怡之/或言怠也  李鼎祚作</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='466:492'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '012-2a' );" name="012-2a" class="pb">[012-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='492:538'>　<span class='krp-note'>怡平項安世曰怡時災來于韻為協然怠字何嘗不/協  上去入之分自沈約始豫怠二字本是古語</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='538:548'>噬嗑食也賁无色也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='548:560'>　食晁說之曰食一作合</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='560:568'>兌見而巽伏也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='568:584'>　見鄭𤣥作說<span class='krp-note'>本晁/說之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='584:594'>隨无故也蠱則飭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='594:634'>　飭鄭𤣥虞翻王肅作飾<span class='krp-note'>一本作節誤宗李鼎祚作餙/蘇軾李衡王  𫝊李簡王申</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='634:657'>　<span class='krp-note'>子熊良輔同作毛居/正曰飭音敕  餙誤</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='657:683'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '012-2b' );" name="012-2b" class="pb">[012-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='683:691'>剥爛也復反也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='691:700'>晉晝也明夷誅也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='700:717'>　俞琰作明夷昧也<span class='krp-note'>昩誤/作誅</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='717:726'>井通而困相遇也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='726:734'>咸速也恆久也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='734:757'>渙離也節止也解緩也蹇難也暌外也家人内也否泰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='757:763'>反其類也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='763:773'>大壯則止遯則退也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='773:799'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '012-3a' );" name="012-3a" class="pb">[012-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='799:822'>大有衆也同人親也革去故也鼎取新也小過過也中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='822:834'>孚信也豐多故親寡旅也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='834:863'>　衆荀爽作終　荀爽作豐多故親<span class='krp-note'>絶句/</span>寡旅也<span class='krp-note'>句/</span>虞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='863:903'>　翻作豐多故<span class='krp-note'>句/</span>親寡旅也<span class='krp-note'>句陸德明曰衆家以豐多/  故絶句李鼎祚亦无也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='903:950'>　<span class='krp-note'>字毛竒齡云李有也字按今李本亦有也字者廷郭/雍朱子項安世王申子李簡胡炳文林希元楊  筠</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='950:988'>　<span class='krp-note'>陳仁錫張振淵陸時位顧炎武/毛竒齡查慎行成徳同无也字</span>謹案　周易折中无</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='988:1021'>　也字吕祖謙云豐多故今本有也字<span class='krp-note'>韓伯蘇軾朱震/王宗𫝊李衡吳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1021:1058'>　<span class='krp-note'>澄胡一桂董楷董真卿熊良輔/俞琰梁寅洪守美同有也字</span>謹案　周易述義有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1058:1084'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '012-3b' );" name="012-3b" class="pb">[012-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1084:1107'>　也字　項安世曰卦名皆句上旅獨在下者取其韻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1107:1126'>　之叶也以多故對寡親則故非事故之故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1126:1134'>離上而坎下也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1134:1144'>小畜寡也履不處也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1144:1154'>需不進也訟不親也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1154:1177'>大過顛也姤遇也柔遇剛也漸女歸待男行也頤養正</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1177:1200'>也既濟定也歸妹女之終也未濟男之窮也夬决也剛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1200:1214'>決柔也君子道長小人道憂也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1214:1240'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '012-4a' );" name="012-4a" class="pb">[012-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1240:1277'>　姤石經于此獨作遘<span class='krp-note'>鄭𤣥李鼎祚朱震王宗/𫝊同朱震曰遘當作姤</span>　憂鄭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1277:1309'>　𤣥<span class='krp-note'>本晁/説之</span>虞翻作消<span class='krp-note'>李氏鼎祚同廉按/今李本亦作憂</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1309:1332'>　蘇軾改作頤養正也大過顛也姤遇也柔遇剛也夬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1332:1355'>　決也剛決柔也君子道長小人道憂漸女歸待男行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1355:1378'>　也歸妹女之終也既濟定也未濟男之窮也云乾坤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1378:1401'>　至需訟兩兩相從明相反之義大過以下非相從之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1401:1425'>　次𫝊者失之也凡八卦今改正而相從之次相反之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1425:1447'>　義煥然若合符節<span class='krp-note'>朱子𤼵改/本同蘇氏</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1447:1473'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '012-4b' );" name="012-4b" class="pb">[012-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1473:1496'>　蔡淵改作大過顛也頤養正也既濟定也未濟男之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1496:1519'>　窮也歸妹女之終也漸女歸待男行也姤遇也柔遇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1519:1542'>　剛也夬決也剛決柔也君子道長小人道憂也云自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1542:1565'>　大過以下有亂簡案雜卦例皆反對協韻為序今以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1565:1608'>　其例改正<span class='krp-note'>吳氏澄同以邱富國曰今依蔡易讀之則/八卦既得  類從而韻亦叶但不當僭改</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1608:1656'>　<span class='krp-note'>經文耳不董真卿案蘇氏亦有改正自頤大過而下/數卦然  若蔡氏之妥  熊朋來自姤遇也以下後</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1656:1697'>　<span class='krp-note'>儒多以意改定或違對卦之例或失古韻之音/惟蔡氏所改定者為可通故熊氏本同蔡氏</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1697:1720'>　俞琰曰頤養正也大過顛也既濟定也未濟男之窮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1720:1746'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '012-5a' );" name="012-5a" class="pb">[012-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1746:1769'>　也歸妹女之終也漸女歸待男行也姤遇也柔遇剛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1769:1789'>　也夬決也剛決柔也君子道長小人道憂也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1789:1812'>　毛竒齡曰疑改作大過顛也頤養正也漸女歸待男</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1812:1835'>　行也歸妹女之終也既濟定也未濟男之窮也姤遇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1835:1858'>　也柔遇剛也夬決也剛決柔也君子道長小人道憂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1858:1862'>　也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1862:1885'>　晁說之曰鄭云自大過顛也以下卦音不協似錯亂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1885:1894'>　失正弗敢改耳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1894:1920'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '012-5b' );" name="012-5b" class="pb">[012-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1920:1943'>　朱子曰自大過以下卦不反對或疑其錯簡今以韻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1943:1979'>　協之又似非誤未詳何義<span class='krp-note'>胡氏炳文曰本義謂大過/以下疑其錯簡今以韻協</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1979:1990'>　<span class='krp-note'>之又似/非誤</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1990:1993'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1993:1996'>　</span><br/>
